_sText:
### ---Introduction---

Fy_spawnkill is the first map I've ever made. It was mostly meant for trying out some ideas and learning how to build teleports, lightning, and using Source SDK in general.

Somewhere along the way, I broke some textures and alignments using the carve tool. I am aware of this, but it will not be fixed as I would have to remake this entire map. I have learned from my mistakes and am currently working on bigger projects.

### ---How to play---

Shoot the other team, using weapons found throughout the map and utilizing portal teleportation wisely.
